---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Setup / Muhammad Firas" description="Tools, hardware, and servers used by Muhammad Firas.">
	<main id="main-content" class="shell page-shell">
		<section class="stack">
			<h1>Setup</h1>
			<p class="line">-</p>

			<h2>Tools</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Nix + flakes for system and environment management</li>
				<li>Home Manager and nix-darwin for macOS config</li>
				<li>devenv templates: Python, Node.js, Rust, Bun, PHP, Go</li>
				<li>Neovim (AstroNvim) as the main editor</li>
				<li>Core CLI: git, ripgrep, fd, lazygit, uv, pnpm, bun</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Hardware</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Workstation:</strong> manson (macOS, aarch64-darwin)</li>
				<li><strong>Home server:</strong> shisui (Intel i3-2310M, 8GB DDR3, 464GB HDD)</li>
				<li><strong>VPS:</strong> itachi (OVH, 4 vCPU Haswell, 8GB RAM, 75GB disk)</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Servers</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>shisui:</strong> headless NixOS laptop server on local network + Tailscale</li>
				<li><strong>itachi:</strong> remote NixOS VPS installed via nixos-anywhere</li>
				<li>Services stack: Caddy, Nextcloud, Tailscale, SSH</li>
				<li>Deploy flow: `nixos-rebuild switch` with remote build host for Linux targets</li>
			</ul>

			<p class="note">
				This setup is based on: <a href="https://github.com/fear-rush/realm">github.com/fear-rush/realm</a>
			</p>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	.shell {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		min-height: 100vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-start;
		justify-content: center;
		padding: 4.25rem 1.25rem 7rem;
	}

	.stack {
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 70ch;
		text-align: left;
		padding-left: 1.1rem;
		border-left: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
	}

	h1,
	h2,
	p,
	li,
	a,
	strong {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.86rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		letter-spacing: 0.02em;
		line-height: 1.62;
	}

	h2 {
		margin-top: 1.1rem;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.line {
		margin: 1rem 0 0.9rem;
		color: var(--ink-soft);
	}

	ul {
		margin: 0.6rem 0 0;
		padding-left: 1.2rem;
	}

	li + li {
		margin-top: 0.35rem;
	}

	strong {
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.note {
		margin-top: 1.2rem;
		color: var(--ink-soft);
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.shell {
			padding: 1.25rem 1rem 4rem 1.25rem;
		}

		.stack {
			padding-left: 0.85rem;
		}
	}
</style>
